front.title: •Feltipern Trevagg
front.gametext: While no droid present with Trevagg, to initiate battles at same location as Trevagg, player must use X Force, where X = total number of [Dark Side Force] and [Light Side Force] present with him.
front.lore: Corrupt tax collector. A male Gotal. Bounty hunter. Once sought a bounty on Obi-Wan. Has limited sensing ability to droid emanations. Romanced M'iiyoom Onith.

canceledBy: Game text is canceled by Freon Drevan
rulings: Resets the cost of initiating battle, cannot be further modified by cards like Wars Not Make One Great.
Anything allowing battle to be initiated for free ignores this cost.
If inside a starship or enclosed vehicle, the number of Force icons present with Trevagg is 0.
